sub_title: Sales Engineer for Insurance & Banking at Planet
summary:
Coming from Greece, I have studied in Switzerland, currently live in the Netherlands and work for the German entity of a US company, Planet. Obviously I love travelling, meeting and working with people all over the world! 

As an earth observation engineer, I have developed a passion for figuring out solutions that contribute to the climate risk adaptation and management. From improving the climate resilience of farmers across the world to providing insights for timely and efficient response after a natural disaster, satellite imagery can add great value. Because we can't fix what we can't see!
